cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE

The paper discusses a tool for extracting definitions from text, which is a natural language processing task. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The tool also uses machine learning techniques, which suggests categories such as cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the tool is evaluated on a dataset related to neuroscience, which could suggest cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
